{"tid":895569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬女疑不忿「送車尾」　襲龍運車長及站長被捕","createTime":"2018-11-09T09:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T23:42:59.000Z","uid":220701,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1ef1a691a8511bce90799e54a27fc5baa7fce9","tid":895569,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181109/mobile/bkn-20181109131501116-1109_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181109%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181109131501116-1109_00822_001.html&d=VgGdjm0gORkSc%2F0wb7u1sOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=4e335ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181109/mobile/bkn-20181109131501116-1109_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一名姓陳（61歲）女乘客，今晨（9日）11時許，到東涌逸東邨巴士總站，擬乘搭龍運巴士E31線往荃灣，惟有人疑不滿「送車尾」，未能趕上已離站的巴士，向站內的龍運站長及另一名車長投訴，姓黎（56歲）車長解釋因安全理由，巴士已駛離站未能安排上車，陳即發難出手掌摑車長，車長受傷倒地，陳見闖禍欲離開，姓羅（23歲）站長即時阻止，並報警及通知公司，糾纏間站長的右手腕擦傷。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據網上流傳片段可見，站長抓緊陳的左手袖位置，喝令：「咪走呀，企喺度呀」，惟女乘客仍不停掙扎，站長一邊將陳推到牆邊，一邊報警，稱：「佢打車長呀，打埋我」，混亂間，女乘客的衣袖被扯破。救護員趕抵，將車長及站長送院治理，而警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌普通襲擊拘捕陳，帶署扣查，案件交大嶼北分區人員跟進。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九巴及龍運發言人稱，對於有車長和前線同事遇襲，十分憤慨及強烈譴責襲擊的行為，會配合警方的調查，公司法律部會全力協助受襲同事，發言人強調，襲擊車長屬刑事罪行，一經定罪可判罰款及監禁，呼籲乘客切勿以身試法。資料顯示，涉事巴士路線來往東涌逸東邨至荃灣愉景新城。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"09a7e2d23b957bc12154e929e0f7345ba855d8f4","tid":895569,"uid":38041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"東涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3ffc377efaec5111c3fb5137ad7bb5b93827d1","tid":895569,"uid":22683,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e242a508afbe5ebac4875bf28e974bc7689152cf","tid":895569,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"公屋1分"},{"pid":"51a339a8dfc523b3d54a6e916281a6a0fac66edb","tid":895569,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a7e2d23b957bc12154e929e0f7345ba855d8f4","tid":895569,"uid":38041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"東涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"呢排壓力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082123ab8ed81fc503d8893c86ac8f7d9e7766da","tid":895569,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"最尾淆到 個車長識玩"},{"pid":"a2fd96b35b842d6c684d93e77ce7b140bab12cdc","tid":895569,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"抵撚死廢老"},{"pid":"a314357ce31dac05ab0a8e2ec220de399ff33511","tid":895569,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"emax shuffle德福站頭阿姐你不如仆街死啦去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bGbqcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bGbqcS</a><br />\n<br />\n送車尾上連登屌下人咪算<br />\n唔駛郁手郁腳既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2dd2129842c7d19681c9d3e925325b0a571858","tid":895569,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy